WEBVTT

00:06:28.200 --> 00:06:31.440
we'll have almost one billion
mobile phone subscriptions.

00:06:32.040 --> 00:06:34.616
We have the power in our hands

00:06:34.640 --> 00:06:38.896
to ensure that livestock production
systems are not only healthy,

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:40.920
productive and profitable,

00:06:41.600 --> 00:06:43.936
but that farmers are knowledgeable,

00:06:43.960 --> 00:06:45.776
and more importantly,

00:06:45.800 --> 00:06:47.680
that our farmers are safe.

00:06:48.440 --> 00:06:50.016
Working with smallholder farmers

00:06:50.040 --> 00:06:53.040
is one of the best ways
to guarantee food security.

00:06:54.160 --> 00:06:56.816
Working with smallholder farmers
is one of the best ways

00:06:56.840 --> 00:07:00.816
to guarantee each and every child
their full opportunity